After a very successful 2014 (which saw him rise again in the DJ Mag Top 100), and as a follow up to the hugely successful artist album titled 'Find Your Harmony', the 2015 compilation bearing the same name features brand new material from the young Moldovan artist, and some other new, truly gargantuan tunes.
